channel.title: Comments on: Busy couple of months ahead

item.title: By: Kevin Pettitt
item.dc:creator: Kevin Pettitt
item.description: <p>Matt, good luck with the move. We put our house on the market earlier in the year, so I understand what you've been going through as far as "consolidation" goes. Just to get it ready to show required lots of purging.</p>
